      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey im in rio and i think i went too hard in the sun today. my head is spinning a bit and im having a really hard time finding the right words when i talk, like they're just stuck. i feel super confused. is this just dehydration or something? i dont really wanna go to a hospital if i dont have to",
